definitions.definition: ( anatomy ) A pit , groove , cavity , or depression .
( astronomy ) A long, narrow, shallow depression on the body of an extraterrestrial body, such as a planet or moon .

main_definition: ( anatomy ) A pit , groove , cavity , or depression .
secondary_definitions: ( astronomy ) A long, narrow, shallow depression on the body of an extraterrestrial body, such as a planet or moon .

definitions.definition: A large nocturnal reddish-brown catlike mammal ( Cryptoprocta ferox ) of the civet family, endemic to the rainforests of Madagascar . It is slender , long-tailed and has retractile claws and anal scent glands .
